  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一下APB RTC模块的架构图。这个RTC是挂在APB总线上的，最顶层叫apb_rtc，也就是Top Level。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TOP",
        "apb_slave"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以顶层模块同时连接APB总线作为从设备。那除了APB接口，Top Level下面还拆分成哪些主要子模块？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TOP",
        "CFG",
        "CORE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "有两个大分支：一个是rtc_config_regs，负责寄存器配置；另一个是rtc_core，负责真正的RTC功能逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CFG",
        "CORE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我从TOP引出两条线，分别连接到CFG和CORE。接下来先细化寄存器这边？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CFG"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，CFG下面再挂一个rtc_regs，这是用PeakRDL自动生成的寄存器模块，作为Register Wrapper的下一层。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CFG",
        "REGS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：CFG是rtc_config_regs，它包含的是rtc_regs，标注PeakRDL。这样理解对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CFG",
        "REGS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。现在看rtc_core这边，它下面有四个功能单元。第一个是Time Counter，负责从秒到世纪的计数。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CORE",
        "TIME"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Time Counter的标注我写\"seconds to century\"可以吗？另外三个单元是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TIME"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "可以。另外三个是：Alarm Comparator做闹钟比较，Interrupt Generator产生中断，还有BCD Logic处理BCD码转换。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ALARM",
        "INT_GEN",
        "BCD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我从CORE引出四条线，分别连接到Time Counter、Alarm Comparator、Interrupt Generator和BCD Logic。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CORE",
        "TIME",
        "ALARM",
        "INT_GEN",
        "BCD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，BCD Logic这个名字会不会太简略？要不要展开说明一下？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "BCD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "保持BCD Logic就行，图上空间有限。不过Time Counter的括号标注我确认一下是\"seconds to century\"， century是世纪的意思对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TIME"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是支持到世纪的年份计数。还有Interrupt Generator，这个会连到GIC，不过GIC不画在这个图里。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "INT_GEN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "了解，INT_GEN只画到模块边界。我检查一下整体结构：TOP下面有APB、CFG、CORE三条线，CFG下面有REGS，CORE下面有TIME、ALARM、INT_GEN、BCD。完整了吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TOP",
        "CFG",
        "CORE",
        "REGS",
        "TIME",
        "ALARM",
        "INT_GEN",
        "BCD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "APB那条线你写的是APB，但应该标注为apb_slave，表示这是APB从设备接口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TOP",
        "apb_slave"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正，TOP到APB的连接标注改为apb_slave。还有其他需要调整的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TOP",
        "apb_slave"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "REGS的标注，PeakRDL外面要加括号，表示这是工具生成的。另外rtc_config_regs的别名是Register Wrapper，这个也要显示。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CFG",
        "REGS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已更新：CFG显示为rtc_config_regs，别名Register Wrapper；REGS显示rtc_regs，标注(PeakRDL)。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CFG",
        "REGS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "看起来都对了。最后确认一下布局，用TB（从上到下）方向，主题用neutral。",
      "elements_involved": [],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，flowchart TB，neutral主题。所有模块：TOP(apb_rtc Top Level)、CFG(rtc_config_regs Register Wrapper)、REGS(rtc_regs PeakRDL)、CORE(rtc_core)、TIME(Time Counter seconds to century)、ALARM(Alarm Comparator)、INT_GEN(Interrupt Generator)、BCD(BCD Logic)。结构正确吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TOP",
        "CFG",
        "REGS",
        "CORE",
        "TIME",
        "ALARM",
        "INT_GEN",
        "BCD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
